Class Piece

  • java.lang.Object
    • Piece

  • public class Piece
extends java.lang.Object
    The Piece class creates both the flags and the pawns inside this project. It contains data fields for the following; boolean isPawn, boolean isFlag, boolean, isPawnWithFlag, String pawnColor, and String flagColor
